description: A file containing documents concerning the relationship between West Berlin and the European Economic Community (E.E.C.). Subjects covered in the file include alleged violations of the 1971 Quadripartite Agreement, which delayed the signing of trade agreements between the E.E.C. and Eastern European countries; the consequences for Berlin of the planned introduction of a common European passport; Soviet objections to the "communitisation" of Berlin; problems relating to the territorial application clauses in international agreements; and the view that the Treaty of Rome applied to Berlin "in so far as it does not affect the rights and powers of the Allies". Documents in the file include several versions of a draft report on Berlin and the European Communities, covering the legal status of the city, the Soviet view on the situation, analysis of current and foreseeable problems, and practical consequences.
